{"tid":501423,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"香港IT從業員可望薪酬大幅提升","createTime":"2017-12-16T19:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T07:48:05.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f293c3f73f8e29de477f2e63c141def59d14761e","tid":501423,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T19:25:01.000Z","msg":"專才招聘公司Robert Half最新獨立研究指出，全部受訪的本港企業資訊總監(CIO)都計劃在未來12個月內平均為20%的IT員工加薪，預料平均加幅為7.9%，遠高於本港所有行業綜合按年平均升幅3.8%；這對本港IT從業員來說無疑是一大佳音。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1965000/1969862/OGIT_600.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1965000%2F1969862%2FOGIT_600.PNG&h=b165f2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://imoney.hket.com/article/1969862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimoney.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1969862&d=l5NSWSY8HZggNMti%2Ba%2FOoKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d72b979d\" target=\"_blank\">http://imoney.hket.com/article/1969862</a></div>"},{"pid":"f3fef3555f9cfcbd785fbe6d02460521dfeee760","tid":501423,"uid":35815,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T00:37:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d03897bf1e3bdd2f6dad8069fe1365dcbbf1a67d","tid":501423,"uid":144843,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T00:41:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"884dd4d28ef0306bd7c42cb471641273524ecd06","tid":501423,"uid":84436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T00:44:34.000Z","msg":"20%的IT員工 有得加<br />\n<br />\n另外個 80%呢,唔通只加比FG <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244d27c92c7025227be4e93d71d85e0600247f9a","tid":501423,"uid":35092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T00:47:46.000Z","msg":"$8000 -&gt; $8632"},{"pid":"b3b0dd0724cb624c75a755573b0f1554e3b9a4aa","tid":501423,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":